# DevOps Setup Notes — Student Management System

## Summary of All Changes Made

### Issues Fixed (Docker Local Setup)

| # | Issue | Fix |
|---|-------|-----|
| 1 | **Duplicate SecurityConfig** — Two [SecurityConfig.java](file:///c:/Users/dharm/OneDrive/Desktop/full_stack/student-management-backend/src/main/java/com/example/sms/config/SecurityConfig.java) files in `config/` and [security/](file:///c:/Users/dharm/OneDrive/Desktop/full_stack/student-management-backend/src/main/java/com/example/sms/config/SecurityConfig.java#67-85) packages caused Spring Boot bean conflict | Removed the duplicate in [security/](file:///c:/Users/dharm/OneDrive/Desktop/full_stack/student-management-backend/src/main/java/com/example/sms/config/SecurityConfig.java#67-85) package |
| 2 | **MySQL hostname mismatch** — [application.properties](file:///c:/Users/dharm/OneDrive/Desktop/full_stack/student-management-backend/src/main/resources/application.properties) used `mysql-db` but docker-compose service name was `mysql` | Changed to `mysql` everywhere |
| 3 | **Credential mismatch** — Properties used `root/root` but docker-compose set `appuser/app123` | Aligned to `appuser/app123` |
| 4 | **Deprecated Hibernate dialect** — `MySQL8Dialect` deprecated | Changed to `MySQLDialect` |
| 5 | **Frontend build error** — `listCourses` and [getCourse](file:///c:/Users/dharm/OneDrive/Desktop/full_stack/student-management-frontend/src/services/CourseService.js#10-11) not exported from [CourseService.js](file:///c:/Users/dharm/OneDrive/Desktop/full_stack/student-management-frontend/src/services/CourseService.js) | Added export aliases |
| 6 | **No Docker network** — Containers couldn't communicate | Added explicit `app-network` bridge |
| 7 | **API URL mismatch** — Frontend tried `localhost:8080` from Docker | Changed to empty string (relative URL) + Nginx proxy |
| 8 | **[.dockerignore](file:///c:/Users/dharm/OneDrive/Desktop/full_stack/student-management-backend/.dockerignore) issues** — `target/` and `dist/` were not ignored | Fixed to reduce build context size |

